{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_11_01",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日もリズノワは遅くまで練習か。BIG4になって）\n（しばらく経つけど、練習熱心なのは相変わらずだな）",
      "startTime": 5.323598668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのところ、今までで一番合いましたね！\nみなさん、忘れないうちにもう一回やってみませんか？",
      "startTime": 13.6552384694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　いつもの練習風景と少し違うような……）",
      "startTime": 17.5599096935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの莉央さん、すっごくかっこ良かったです！\nでも、左手の振りをもっとこうした方が……",
      "startTime": 26.3567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、そうです！　最高の最高にかっこいいです！\nそんな、私が頼もしいだなんて……えへへ",
      "startTime": 35.5900457382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こころ！　今のところ、なんかしっくり\nこなかったよね。一緒に葵さんに見てもらわない？",
      "startTime": 43.9567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（へぇ……愛が率先して練習を引っ張ってるのか）\n（BIG4になって、心境の変化があったみたいだな）",
      "startTime": 52.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です！\n練習に夢中で気付きませんでした、すみません",
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ついさっき来たばかりだから気にしないでくれ\nそれよりMV撮影に向けてレッスン、頑張ってるな",
      "startTime": 67.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "頑張り屋なのは相変わらずだが\nBIG4になってからの愛は凄く頼もしいよ",
      "startTime": 74.1251970269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうですか？\n頼もしいって言葉、今は一番嬉しいかもしれません",
      "startTime": 80.3298414866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』が始まった頃は\n莉央さんと葵さんを支えるのが役目だと思ってました",
      "startTime": 87.7965081532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "でもセミファイナルのステージの前に\nこころと話して、少し考えが変わったんです",
      "startTime": 94.7631748199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "支えるんじゃなく、自分こそがLizNoirだ\nお二人と本当の意味で並んで立つんだ！　……って",
      "startTime": 102.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "だから今は、莉央さんや葵さんの背中を\n追いかけるだけの、ただの後輩じゃなくて",
      "startTime": 108.9965081532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "隣に並ぶ仲間として、頼りにしてもらえるように\n出来ることは積極的にやろうと思ってるんです",
      "startTime": 116.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……大きく意識が変わったんだな\n俺の目から見ても、愛は凄く成長していると思う",
      "startTime": 124.5224657078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "褒めていただけて嬉しいです！\n試行錯誤した甲斐がありました",
      "startTime": 131.3342239864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "試行錯誤？　どんなことをしたんだ？\n良かったら俺にも教えてくれ",
      "startTime": 138.2999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、強靭な精神は強靭な肉体に宿ると思って\nまずは筋トレを二倍に増やしました！",
      "startTime": 145.2979102452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "に、二倍！？\nそれは……オーバーワークになってないか？",
      "startTime": 150.1999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大丈夫です！\nちゃんと、自分の調子を見ながらメニューを決めました",
      "startTime": 156.1818095843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "それから、格闘技の体験教室に行ってみたんです\n体験だけでも気が引き締まりましたよ～",
      "startTime": 163.9818095843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "か、格闘技！？　鍛えることに本当に妥協がないな\n怪我が少し心配だが……",
      "startTime": 172.5999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……というか、格闘技の楽しさに目覚めて\nそっちの道に進む、なんてことはない……よな？",
      "startTime": 178.4228634593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そんなことありえません！　それに今は\n時間が取れないから、本格的に習うのは見送りました",
      "startTime": 187.9952335992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、凄く勉強になりました。声を出すことの大切さや\n体の動きの一つ一つに意図を持たせることとか",
      "startTime": 197.14979895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。そんな試行錯誤が\n愛の成長に繋がっているんだな",
      "startTime": 204.4333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "今は、LizNoirのためにもっと何かしたくて\n自分に出来ることを探してる最中なんです",
      "startTime": 211.0019572892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "それで……あの、{user}さん\n大変厚かましいんですが、一つお願いがあって……",
      "startTime": 219.0686239558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "その、私に……やらせてほしいことが、あるんです",
      "startTime": 225.06859649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 232.2790611754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.2790611754
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.2790611754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、この間の件ですけど……\nリズノワのみんなと話し合ってきました",
      "startTime": 237.4475336595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "おお、早速聞いてきたんだな\nそれで、結果は……",
      "startTime": 243.4337649774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.0145282279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "はい、僭越ではありますが……今度のMV撮影\n私、小美山愛がリードさせていただきます！",
      "startTime": 251.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 254.6791765064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、最近の私は頼りになるからって\n快く任せて下さったんです",
      "startTime": 258.1413093247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "その期待に応えるためにも\n最高のMVを作ってみせますから、期待してて下さい！",
      "startTime": 263.2079861639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
